: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Askerî komuta-kontrol, haberleşme ve elektronik\r\nharp sistemleri, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Askerî uzay sistemleri, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Askerî keşif, gözetleme ve seyrüsefer\r\nsistemleri, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Balistik koruma sistemleri ile diğer askerî\r\nmalzeme ve teknolojiler. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b>İzin\r\nSüreçleri<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">Liste\r\nkapsamında bulunan ürünlerin;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Üretimi, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->İthalatı, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->İhracatı <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">ile <b>Füze\r\nTeknolojisi Kontrol Rejimi (MTCR)</b> ve <b>Wassenaar Düzenlemesi Mühimmat\r\nListesi</b> kapsamındaki izin işlemleri <b>Millî Savunma Bakanlığının\r\nsorumluluğunda ve bilgisi dâhilinde</b> yürütülecektir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b>Geçiş\r\nHükümleri<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">2023 yılı\r\nKontrole Tabi Malzeme Listesinde yer almamakla birlikte 2026 yılı Listesine ilk\r\nkez dahil edilen ürünleri hâlihazırda üreten kuruluşlar için önemli geçiş\r\nhükümleri öngörülmüştür.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">Bu kapsamda;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Liste kapsamına yeni giren ürünleri üreten\r\nkuruluşların, Listenin yayımlandığı tarihten itibaren <b>2 ay içerisinde</b>\r\nKişi Güvenlik Belgesi, Tesis Güvenlik Belgesi, Kuruluş İzni ve Üretim İzin\r\nBelgesi süreçlerine başvurmaları gerekmektedir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Belgelendirme sürecinin <b>1 Haziran 2027</b>\r\ntarihine kadar tamamlanması öngörülmektedir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Başvuruda bulunan kuruluşlar, belgelendirme\r\nsüreci tamamlanıncaya kadar mevcut üretim faaliyetlerine <b>1 Haziran 2027</b>\r\ntarihine kadar devam edebilecektir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Belgelendirme sürecine dahil olmak istemeyen\r\nkuruluşların ise mevcut stoklarını <b>en geç 1 Haziran 2027</b> tarihine kadar\r\nsatışa konu etmeleri gerekmektedir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b>Dikkat\r\nEdilmesi Gereken Hususlar<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">Liste\r\nkapsamında ayrıca;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Çift kullanımlı (dual-use) malzemelere ilişkin\r\nişlemlerin ilgili mevzuat kapsamında yürütüleceği, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Gümrük beyannamelerinde eşyanın askerî veya\r\nsivil amaçlı olduğunun beyan edilmesinin zorunlu olduğu, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Herhangi bir ürünün Liste kapsamında bulunup\r\nbulunmadığına ilişkin tereddütlerde <b>Millî Savunma Bakanlığının kararının\r\nesas alınacağı</b> hüküm altına alınmıştır. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b>Yürürlük<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b>2026 Yılı\r\nKontrole Tâbi Malzeme Listesi yayımı tarihinde yürürlüğe girmiş olup, hükümleri\r\nMillî Savunma Bakanı tarafından yürütülecektir.</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">Kaynak: <a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/06/20260630-2.htm\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/06/20260630-2.htm</a></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
